{"type": "article", "id": 5115, "title": "Nike 运动鞋 Metcon 1", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-12T07:55:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135238c3zeHw7KhStR9Pid.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t耐克日前推出一款全新的运动鞋 Metcon 1，这款全新的运动鞋配备了 Flywire 结构系统与双密度鞋底，Flywire 结构系统用于灵活地稳定脚掌，双密度鞋底则用于提升鞋的整体安全性，不管是进行力量训练、跑步还是弹跳，都能够起到足够的减震效果。此外， Metcon 1 的鞋面部分选用了网眼物料制作而成，舒服透气。定价 120 美元（约合人民币 745 元），1 月 31 日将于 <a href=\"http://www.nike.com/us/en_us/c/launch/2015-01/nike-metcon-1\" target=\"_blank\">Nike 线上商店</a>正式发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135235BN2qYvpGQi5oSCPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135236WpSMjQseKZ7IrcCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135236YEZlgTjyJLdP6nXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.534375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061352366rJKGXlguUNpCO3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135237j08BGdF2cYMZluiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}